name: Cut the rope - PEWDIEPIE EDITION
description:
Do you know what lack to the original "cut the rope" ? Pewdiepie references ! That's what !

Well don't search more ! This game got it all !

==========

I made this for a school project where we add to make a "cut the rope" from scratch with Unity. It took me 2 weeks (during holidays so I worked less than 2 week but I didn't count so... Meh) and I hope you'll enjoy the nice 2 minutes gameplay this game has to offer !

And you can join my discord
